    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s absolutely pristine! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been kept in a garage, smells like new, and drives like a dream. I\u2019m only selling it because I\u2019m downsizing, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Everything is in tip-top shape and ready for your next road trip. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
